# Babylon Labs Documentation
> Babylon's Bitcoin staking protocol enables BTC holders to stake their Bitcoin directly on consumer systems (Bitcoin Supercharged Networks) without third-party custody, bridges, or wrapping. The protocol provides BTC-backed economic security guarantees and is designed as a modular plug-in compatible with various consumer systems.
